I"<h2 id="i-am-pizzatarian-billboard-campaign">“I am Pizzatarian” Billboard Campaign</h2>

<p>Campaign launched to promote Bacaro brand awareness around the Montreal area.</p>

<p><img src="/images/portfolio/bacaro/pizzaterien.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>When I first began working on the brand, it had a more classic and old-school look, with branding that did little to differentiate it. Another designer and I worked together to update the brand with a more modern and recognizable visual identity.</p>

